Class Payroll

java.lang.Object
  Payroll

public class Payroll
extends java.lang.Object

Payroll holds methods that will read in a file containing emmployees, outputs employee list, number of employees, women employees, those making =< 35,000 and working with company for =< 5 years, employees given a raise, list sorted in alphavetical order, updated list after employees are hired and fired to terminal window and output file.
